<h2>Dear <%= @order.name %></h2>

<p>Thank you for your recent order from Market.<br/>

 You ordered the following items:<br/>

<table>
  <%=h @order.line_items.each do |line_item| %>
    <tr>
      <td><%= line_item.quantity %> &times;</td>
      <td><%= line_item.product.title %></td>
      <td class="item_price"> <%= number_to_currency(line_item.total_price) %></td>
    </tr>
  <% end %>
</table>


We'll send you a separate e-mail when your order ships.</p>